       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. PAYY2K.
       AUTHOR. SID WAITE.
       DATE-COMPILED. TODAY.
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
       FILE-CONTROL.
           SELECT PAYCUR ASSIGN TO "S30" ORGANIZATION IS INDEXED
           ACCESS MODE IS DYNAMIC RECORD KEY IS PAYCUR-KEY.
           SELECT OLDPAYCUR ASSIGN TO "S35"
           ORGANIZATION LINE SEQUENTIAL.
       DATA DIVISION.
       FILE SECTION.
       FD  OLDPAYCUR.
       01  OLDPAYCUR01.
           02 OLDPAYCUR-KEY.
             03 PC-KEY8 PIC X(8).
             03 PC-KEY3 PIC XXX.
           02 PC-AMOUNT PIC S9(4)V99.
           02 PC-PAYCODE PIC XXX.
           02 PC-DENIAL PIC XX.
           02 PC-CLAIM PIC X(6).
           02 OLDPC-DATE-T PIC X(6).
           02 OLDPC-DATE-E PIC X(6).
       FD  PAYCUR.
       01  PAYCUR01.
           02 PAYCUR-KEY.
             03 PC-KEY8 PIC X(8).
             03 PC-KEY3 PIC XXX.
           02 PC-AMOUNT PIC S9(4)V99.
           02 PC-PAYCODE PIC XXX.
           02 PC-DENIAL PIC XX.
           02 PC-CLAIM PIC X(6).
           02 PC-DATE-TCC PIC XX.
           02 PC-DATE-T PIC X(6).
           02 PC-DATE-ECC PIC XX.
           02 PC-DATE-E PIC X(6).
           02 PC-BATCH PIC X(6).
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       P0.
           OPEN I-O PAYCUR INPUT OLDPAYCUR.
       P1. READ OLDPAYCUR AT END GO TO P2.
           MOVE CORR OLDPAYCUR01 TO PAYCUR01
           MOVE OLDPAYCUR-KEY TO PAYCUR-KEY
           MOVE OLDPC-DATE-T TO PC-DATE-T
           MOVE OLDPC-DATE-E TO PC-DATE-E
           MOVE SPACE TO PC-BATCH.
           IF PC-DATE-T = "000000" MOVE "00" TO PC-DATE-TCC
           ELSE MOVE "19" TO PC-DATE-TCC.
           IF PC-DATE-E = "000000" MOVE "00" TO PC-DATE-ECC
           ELSE MOVE "19" TO PC-DATE-ECC.
           WRITE PAYCUR01 GO TO P1.
       P2.
           CLOSE PAYCUR OLDPAYCUR.
           DISPLAY "RESTORE OF PAYCUR COMPLETED".
           STOP RUN.
